src/graphql/resolvers/noteResolvers.ts
src/graphql/resolvers/userResolvers.ts
src/graphql/dataloaders/noteLoader.ts
src/graphql/context.ts           - GraphQL context
src/graphql/server.ts            - Apollo Server setup
src/graphql/directives/auth.ts   - Auth directive
```

**Practice Exercise:**
- Query notes with nested user data
- Implement real-time note updates via subscriptions
- Compare GraphQL vs REST performance

