## 🟣 Level 5: PRODUCTION-GRADE (Weeks 9-10)

### 5.1 NGINX & Reverse Proxy
**Why Learn This Now**: Production deployment architecture.

**Concepts to Master:**
- Reverse proxy configuration
- Load balancing
- SSL/TLS termination
- Response caching
- Rate limiting at proxy level
- Gzip compression

**Implementation Tasks:**
1. Install and configure NGINX
2. Setup reverse proxy to Node.js
3. Configure SSL certificates
4. Implement proxy caching
5. Add load balancing (multiple Node instances)
6. Configure rate limiting

**Files to Create:**
